  "text": "The results of Davidson and coworkers (Davidson et al. 2006a,b; [CITATION_1] ) provide an interesting connection between the inertial subrange and the scales above r/z ∼ 1 for the second-order structure functions. Insights relating exponents and prefactors in the respective scaling laws were obtained by properly matching the two behaviours at scales when r/z ∼ 1.",
